/data/
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# Frontend (SolidJS + Vite). Source lives in frontend/; the compiled bundle
# is generated and never committed (plan Guardrail #6).
/frontend/node_modules/
/frontend/dist/
# Vite build output — embedded by the Go binary at build time, not committed.
# The whole static/ dir is generated now (Stage 5 cutover removed the old
# tracked static/index.html): `pnpm build` populates it, and a bare
# `go build ./cmd/sakms` fails cleanly on the empty dir until it does.
/internal/web/static/

# Static aria2c binary — a multi-MB platform artifact fetched by
# `make aria2c` (cmd/download-aria2c), never committed. `//go:embed
# assets/aria2c` (internal/downloader/embed.go) fails cleanly until it's
# fetched, same generated-artifact precedent as the frontend bundle above.
# The Dockerfile fetches it in a build stage before `go build`.
/internal/downloader/assets/aria2c

/sakms
/sakms-node
/bin/

/.omc/
.omc/
/.claude/
.claude/
